{"title":"荐歌：明智之举（许嵩）","slug":"荐歌：明智之举（许嵩）","date":"2022-06-24T09:54:53.000Z","updated":"2022-06-24T10:06:00.932Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/荐歌：明智之举（许嵩）.json","excerpt":"文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。荐歌：明智之举（许嵩）周末愉快！毕业季，离别季。<br>","covers":null,"content":"<blockquote>\n<p>文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>荐歌：明智之举（许嵩）</p>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=330 height=86 src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=862099032&auto=1&height=66\"></iframe>\n\n<p>周末愉快！</p>\n<p>毕业季，离别季。<br><span id=\"more\"></span></p>\n<p>高考成绩陆陆续续的都出了，是去大学还是再战一年也有了答案。大四的学生们也该离开校园，独自面对社会。</p>\n<p>“分别”如约而至。或许一别就是很多很多年了。</p>\n<p>今天推荐的歌曲是《明智之举》，来自许嵩。</p>\n<p>歌词的内容或许就是高中毕业生们的接下来的日常，是大学毕业生感同身受的难过过往。就在歌曲里短暂的沉浸，再走出来面对真实的生活吧~</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">作词 : 许嵩</span><br><span class=\"line\">作曲 : 许嵩</span><br><span class=\"line\">编曲 : Adam Lee</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">你在北方某城很偶尔下雨</span><br><span class=\"line\">我在天南海北很偶尔想你</span><br><span class=\"line\">写不来十八九岁煽情字句</span><br><span class=\"line\">孤单喂饱了理性</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">想必你也看过了一些风景</span><br><span class=\"line\">才明白什么样的适合自己</span><br><span class=\"line\">翻着你朋友圈的幸福合影</span><br><span class=\"line\">由衷地为你高兴</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">我曾在意的你</span><br><span class=\"line\">想说声对不起</span><br><span class=\"line\">年少时的任性</span><br><span class=\"line\">有些话伤人不轻</span><br><span class=\"line\">也怀疑自己</span><br><span class=\"line\">不是理想伴侣</span><br><span class=\"line\">你的离开也许是个明智之举</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">我曾在意的你</span><br><span class=\"line\">给过太多悲喜</span><br><span class=\"line\">承蒙时光洗礼</span><br><span class=\"line\">往事已云淡风轻</span><br><span class=\"line\">当我们老去</span><br><span class=\"line\">品尝丰盛回忆</span><br><span class=\"line\">每一道失去都是醇厚的赐予</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">你曾笑着问我</span><br><span class=\"line\">如若重新来过</span><br><span class=\"line\">结局会不会不同</span><br><span class=\"line\">我出神了许久</span><br><span class=\"line\">神游在初见的午后</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>都看到这儿了，不如关注每日推送的“科文路”、互动起来~</strong></p>\n<p><strong>至少点个赞再走吧~</strong></p>\n","more":"</p>\n<p>高考成绩陆陆续续的都出了，是去大学还是再战一年也有了答案。大四的学生们也该离开校园，独自面对社会。</p>\n<p>“分别”如约而至。或许一别就是很多很多年了。</p>\n<p>今天推荐的歌曲是《明智之举》，来自许嵩。</p>\n<p>歌词的内容或许就是高中毕业生们的接下来的日常，是大学毕业生感同身受的难过过往。就在歌曲里短暂的沉浸，再走出来面对真实的生活吧~</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</